00:10:21.906 --> 00:10:24.866 A:middle
Why is it that Messages separate

00:10:25.016 --> 00:10:26.706 A:middle
all these groups in different

00:10:26.706 --> 00:10:27.936 A:middle
conv-- different conversation in

