00:11:18.396 --> 00:11:20.316 A:middle
So what does-- what is the

00:11:20.316 --> 00:11:21.386 A:middle
lesson that we learned from

00:11:21.386 --> 00:11:22.016 A:middle
Messages?

00:11:22.676 --> 00:11:24.456 A:middle
Create groups for meaningful,

00:11:24.586 --> 00:11:25.816 A:middle
